---
/* src/components/ParentSection.astro */
---
<section class="parent-section">
  <div class="container bg-glass parent-box">
    <div class="parent-content">
      <h2>A Thought for <span class="text-accent">Every Parent</span></h2>
      <p class="intro">Are you facing any of these as a parent?</p>
      
      <div class="parent-grid">
        <div class="pain-point">
          <span class="cross">✕</span>
          <p>Child prefers screens over outdoor play?</p>
        </div>
        <div class="pain-point">
          <span class="cross">✕</span>
          <p>Gets tired easily and avoids activity?</p>
        </div>
        <div class="pain-point">
          <span class="cross">✕</span>
          <p>Feels shy in group settings?</p>
        </div>
        <div class="pain-point">
          <span class="cross">✕</span>
          <p>Has energy, but no structured outlet?</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="solution-card">
        <p>If even one of these sounds familiar, you're not alone. And that's exactly why <strong>PlayFT Jr.</strong> was created.</p>
        <a href="tel:+919910128756" class="btn-primary">Let's Discuss Your Child's Growth</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .parent-section {
    padding: 6rem 0;
  }

  .parent-box {
    padding: 5rem;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .parent-content {
    text-align: center;
    max-width: 900px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  h2 {
    font-size: 3rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .text-accent {
    color: var(--color-accent);
  }

  .intro {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    margin-bottom: 4rem;
  }

  .parent-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    gap: 3rem;
    text-align: left;
    margin-bottom: 5rem;
  }

  .pain-point {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 1.5rem;
    padding: 1.5rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
  }

  .cross {
    color: #ef4444;
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    font-weight: 800;
  }

  .pain-point p {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .solution-card {
    background: rgba(247, 134, 61, 0.05); /* Brand Orange at 5% opacity */
    padding: 3rem;
    border-radius: var(--radius-md);
    border: 1px dashed var(--color-primary);
  }

  .solution-card p {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .parent-box {
      padding: 3rem 1.5rem;
    }
    .parent-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 1rem;
    }
    .pain-point {
      padding: 1rem 0;
    }
  }
</style>
